|----------|-------|--------|
| **CRITICAL** | No Authentication | Implement JWT/OAuth |
| **CRITICAL** | HTTP-only (no TLS) | Use HTTPS with SSL/TLS certificates |
| **HIGH** | No Security Headers | Add `helmet` middleware |
| **HIGH** | Exposed Sensitive Data | Implement field-level access control |
| **MEDIUM** | No Rate Limiting | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| **MEDIUM** | No CORS Config | Define explicit CORS policy |
| **MEDIUM** | No Input Validation | Add schema validation (joi/yup) |
| **MEDIUM** | No Error Logging | Implement structured logging (Winston) |
| **MEDIUM** | Outdated Dependencies | Pin versions and audit regularly |

